  "taskId": "task_1778170553664_852",
  "requestedModel": "anti-claude-sonnet-4.6-thinking",
  "text": "문서를 확인했습니다.\n로그인 페이지와 회원가입 페이지 간의 이동이 가능하도록 라우팅 기능을 구현했습니다. 이제 각 페이지 하단의 링크를 클릭하면 새로고침 없이 해당 페이지로 전환됩니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"index.html\",\n    \"content\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"ko\\\">\\n<head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n    <title>SOCIAN 광고주센터</title>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\\\"></script>\\n    <style>\\n        body { \\n            background-color: #f3f4f6; \\n        }\\n    </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n    <div id=\\\"root\\\"></div>\\n\\n    <script type=\\\"text/babel\\\">\\n        // --- Helper Components (Shared) ---\\n        const InputField = ({ id, type, label, value, onChange, placeholder, icon }) => (\\n            <div>\\n                <label htmlFor={id} className=\\\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\\\">\\n                    {label}\\n                </label>\\n                <div className=\\\"mt-1 relative rounded-md shadow-sm\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none\\\">\\n                       {icon}\\n                    </div>\\n                    <input\\n                        type={type}\\n                        id={id}\\n                        name={id}\\n                        value={value}\\n                        onChange={onChange}\\n                        className=\\\"block w-full pl-10 pr-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-[#076cf0] focus:border-[#076cf0] sm:text-sm\\\"\\n                        placeholder={placeholder}\\n                        required\\n                    />\\n                </div>\\n            </div>\\n        );\\n\\n        const UserIcon = () => (\\n            <svg className=\\\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 20 20\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">\\n                <path fillRule=\\\"evenodd\\\" d=\\\"M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z\\\" clipRule=\\\"evenodd\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n        );\\n\\n        const EmailIcon = () => (\\n            <svg className=\\\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 20 20\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">\\n                <path d=\\\"M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z\\\" />\\n                <path d=\\\"M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n        );\\n\\n        const LockIcon = () => (\\n             <svg className=\\\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 20 20\\\" fill=\\\"currentColor\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">\\n                <path fillRule=\\\"evenodd\\\" d=\\\"M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z\\\" clipRule=\\\"evenodd\\\" />\\n            </svg>\\n        );\\n\\n        // --- Page Components ---\\n\\n        const LoginPage = ({ navigateTo }) => {\\n            const [email, setEmail] = React.useState('');\\n            const [password, setPassword] = React.useState('');\\n\\n            const handleSubmit = (e) => {\\n                e.preventDefault();\\n                console.log('Login attempt:', { email, password });\\n                alert(`로그인 시도:\\\\nEmail: ${email}`);\\n            };\\n\\n            return (\\n                <div className=\\\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"max-w-md w-full space-y-8 bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg\\\">\\n                        <div>\\n                            <h2 className=\\\"mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900\\\">\\n                                SOCIAN 광고주센터\\n                            </h2>\\n                            <p className=\\\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\\\">\\n                                계정에 로그인하세요\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <form className=\\\"mt-8 space-y-6\\\" onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\\n                            <div className=\\\"rounded-md shadow-sm -space-y-px flex flex-col gap-y-4\\\">\\n                                <InputField \\n                                    id=\\\"email\\\"\\n                                    type=\\\"email\\\"\\n                                    label=\\\"이메일 주소\\\"\\n                                    value={email}\\n                                    onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}\\n                                    placeholder=\\\"you@example.com\\\"\\n                                    icon={<EmailIcon />}\\n                                />\\n                                <InputField \\n                                    id=\\\"password\\\"\\n                                    type=\\\"password\\\"\\n                                    label=\\\"비밀번호\\\"\\n                                    value={password}\\n                                    onChange={(e) => setPassword(e.target.value)}\\n                                    placeholder=\\\"Password\\\"\\n                                    icon={<LockIcon />}\\n                                />\\n                            </div>\\n\\n                            <div className=\\\"flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n                                <div className=\\\"text-sm\\\">\\n                                    <a href=\\\"#\\\" className=\\\"font-medium text-[#076cf0] hover:text-[#4834fd]\\\">\\n                                        비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?\\n                                    </a>\\n                                </div>\\n                            </div>\\n\\n                            <div>\\n                                <button\\n                                    type=\\\"submit\\\"\\n                                    className=\\\"group relative w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-[#076cf0] hover:bg-[#4834fd] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#4834fd]\\\"\\n                                >\\n                                    로그인\\n                                </button>\\n                            </div>\\n                        </form>\\n                        <div className=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n                             <p className=\\\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\\\">\\n                                계정이 없으신가요?{' '}\\n                                <a href=\\\"#\\\" onClick={(e) => { e.preventDefault(); navigateTo('register'); }} className=\\\"font-medium text-[#076cf0] hover:text-[#4834fd]\\\">\\n                                    회원가입\\n                                </a>\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        const RegistrationPage = ({ navigateTo }) => {\\n            const [name, setName] = React.useState('');\\n            const [email, setEmail] = React.useState('');\\n            const [password, setPassword] = React.useState('');\\n            const [confirmPassword, setConfirmPassword] = React.useState('');\\n\\n            const handleSubmit = (e) => {\\n                e.preventDefault();\\n                if (password !== confirmPassword) {\\n                    alert('비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.');\\n                    return;\\n                }\\n                console.log('Registration attempt:', { name, email, password });\\n                alert(`회원가입 시도:\\\\nName: ${name}\\\\nEmail: ${email}`);\\n            };\\n\\n            return (\\n                <div className=\\\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"max-w-md w-full space-y-8 bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg\\\">\\n                        <div>\\n                            <h2 className=\\\"mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900\\\">\\n                                SOCIAN 광고주센터\\n                            </h2>\\n                            <p className=\\\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\\\">\\n                                새 계정을 생성하세요\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <form className=\\\"mt-8 space-y-6\\\" onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\\n                            <div className=\\\"rounded-md shadow-sm -space-y-px flex flex-col gap-y-4\\\">\\n                                <InputField \\n                                    id=\\\"name\\\"\\n                                    type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                                    label=\\\"이름\\\"\\n                                    value={name}\\n                                    onChange={(e) => setName(e.target.value)}\\n                                    placeholder=\\\"홍길동\\\"\\n                                    icon={<UserIcon />}\\n                                />\\n                                <InputField \\n                                    id=\\\"email-register\\\"\\n                                    type=\\\"email\\\"\\n                                    label=\\\"이메일 주소\\\"\\n                                    value={email}\\n                                    onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}\\n                                    placeholder=\\\"you@example.com\\\"\\n                                    icon={<EmailIcon />}\\n                                />\\n                                <InputField \\n                                    id=\\\"password-register\\\"\\n                                    type=\\\"password\\\"\\n                                    label=\\\"비밀번호\\\"\\n                                    value={password}\\n                                    onChange={(e) => setPassword(e.target.value)}\\n                                    placeholder=\\\"Password\\\"\\n                                    icon={<LockIcon />}\\n                                />\\n                                <InputField \\n                                    id=\\\"confirm-password\\\"\\n                                    type=\\\"password\\\"\\n                                    label=\\\"비밀번호 확인\\\"\\n                                    value={confirmPassword}\\n                                    onChange={(e) => setConfirmPassword(e.target.value)}\\n                                    placeholder=\\\"Confirm Password\\\"\\n                                    icon={<LockIcon />}\\n                                />\\n                            </div>\\n\\n                            <div>\\n                                <button\\n                                    type=\\\"submit\\\"\\n                                    className=\\\"group relative w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-[#076cf0] hover:bg-[#4834fd] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#4834fd] mt-6\\\"\\n                                >\\n                                    회원가입\\n                                </button>\\n                            </div>\\n                        </form>\\n                        <div className=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n                             <p className=\\\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\\\">\\n                                이미 계정이 있으신가요?{' '}\\n                                <a href=\\\"#\\\" onClick={(e) => { e.preventDefault(); navigateTo('login'); }} className=\\\"font-medium text-[#076cf0] hover:text-[#4834fd]\\\">\\n                                    로그인\\n                                </a>\\n                            </p>\\n                        </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        // --- Main App Component (Router) ---\\n        const App = () => {\\n            const [currentPage, setCurrentPage] = React.useState('login'); // or 'register'\\n\\n            const navigate = (page) => {\\n                setCurrentPage(page);\\n            };\\n\\n            if (currentPage === 'login') {\\n                return <LoginPage navigateTo={navigate} />;\\n            }\\n\\n            if (currentPage === 'register') {\\n                return <RegistrationPage navigateTo={navigate} />;\\n            }\\n\\n            return <div>Page not found</div>;\\n        };\\n\\n        ReactDOM.render(<App />, document.getElementById('root'));\\n    </script>\\n</body>\\n</html>\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ko\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SOCIAN 광고주센터</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\"></script>\n    <style>\n        body { \n            background-color: #f3f4f6; \n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"root\"></div>\n\n    <script type=\"text/babel\">\n        // --- Helper Components (Shared) ---\n        const InputField = ({ id, type, label, value, onChange, placeholder, icon }) => (\n            <div>\n                <label htmlFor={id} className=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\">\n                    {label}\n                </label>\n                <div className=\"mt-1 relative rounded-md shadow-sm\">\n                    <div className=\"absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none\">\n                       {icon}\n                    </div>\n                    <input\n                        type={type}\n                        id={id}\n                        name={id}\n                        value={value}\n                        onChange={onChange}\n                        className=\"block w-full pl-10 pr-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-[#076cf0] focus:border-[#076cf0] sm:text-sm\"\n                        placeholder={placeholder}\n                        required\n                    />\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        );\n\n        const UserIcon = () => (\n            <svg className=\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <path fillRule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z\" clipRule=\"evenodd\" />\n            </svg>\n        );\n\n        const EmailIcon = () => (\n            <svg className=\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <path d=\"M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z\" />\n                <path d=\"M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z\" />\n            </svg>\n        );\n\n        const LockIcon = () => (\n             <svg className=\"h-5 w-5 text-gray-400\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <path fillRule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z\" clipRule=\"evenodd\" />\n            </svg>\n        );\n\n        // --- Page Components ---\n\n        const LoginPage = ({ navigateTo }) => {\n            const [email, setEmail] = React.useState('');\n            const [password, setPassword] = React.useState('');\n\n            const handleSubmit = (e) => {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                console.log('Login attempt:', { email, password });\n                alert(`로그인 시도:\\nEmail: ${email}`);\n            };\n\n            return (\n                <div className=\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n                    <div className=\"max-w-md w-full space-y-8 bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h2 className=\"mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900\">\n                                SOCIAN 광고주센터\n                            </h2>\n                            <p className=\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                                계정에 로그인하세요\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <form className=\"mt-8 space-y-6\" onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\n                            <div className=\"rounded-md shadow-sm -space-y-px flex flex-col gap-y-4\">\n                                <InputField \n                                    id=\"email\"\n                                    type=\"email\"\n                                    label=\"이메일 주소\"\n                                    value={email}\n                                    onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}\n                                    placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n                                    icon={<EmailIcon />}\n                                />\n                                <InputField \n                                    id=\"password\"\n                                    type=\"password\"\n                                    label=\"비밀번호\"\n                                    value={password}\n                                    onChange={(e) => setPassword(e.target.value)}\n                                    placeholder=\"Password\"\n                                    icon={<LockIcon />}\n                                />\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                                <div className=\"text-sm\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" className=\"font-medium text-[#076cf0] hover:text-[#4834fd]\">\n                                        비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div>\n                                <button\n                                    type=\"submit\"\n                                    className=\"group relative w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-[#076cf0] hover:bg-[#4834fd] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#4834fd]\"\n                                >\n                                    로그인\n                                </button>\n                            </div>\n                        </form>\n                        <div className=\"text-center\">\n                             <p className=\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                                계정이 없으신가요?{' '}\n                                <a href=\"#\" onClick={(e) => { e.preventDefault(); navigateTo('register'); }} className=\"font-medium text-[#076cf0] hover:text-[#4834fd]\">\n                                    회원가입\n                                </a>\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        const RegistrationPage = ({ navigateTo }) => {\n            const [name, setName] = React.useState('');\n            const [email, setEmail] = React.useState('');\n            const [password, setPassword] = React.useState('');\n            const [confirmPassword, setConfirmPassword] = React.useState('');\n\n            const handleSubmit = (e) => {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                if (password !== confirmPassword) {\n                    alert('비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.');\n                    return;\n                }\n                console.log('Registration attempt:', { name, email, password });\n                alert(`회원가입 시도:\\nName: ${name}\\nEmail: ${email}`);\n            };\n\n            return (\n                <div className=\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n                    <div className=\"max-w-md w-full space-y-8 bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h2 className=\"mt-6 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900\">\n                                SOCIAN 광고주센터\n                            </h2>\n                            <p className=\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                                새 계정을 생성하세요\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <form className=\"mt-8 space-y-6\" onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\n                            <div className=\"rounded-md shadow-sm -space-y-px flex flex-col gap-y-4\">\n                                <InputField \n                                    id=\"name\"\n                                    type=\"text\"\n                                    label=\"이름\"\n                                    value={name}\n                                    onChange={(e) => setName(e.target.value)}\n                                    placeholder=\"홍길동\"\n                                    icon={<UserIcon />}\n                                />\n                                <InputField \n                                    id=\"email-register\"\n                                    type=\"email\"\n                                    label=\"이메일 주소\"\n                                    value={email}\n                                    onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}\n                                    placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n                                    icon={<EmailIcon />}\n                                />\n                                <InputField \n                                    id=\"password-register\"\n                                    type=\"password\"\n                                    label=\"비밀번호\"\n                                    value={password}\n                                    onChange={(e) => setPassword(e.target.value)}\n                                    placeholder=\"Password\"\n                                    icon={<LockIcon />}\n                                />\n                                <InputField \n                                    id=\"confirm-password\"\n                                    type=\"password\"\n                                    label=\"비밀번호 확인\"\n                                    value={confirmPassword}\n                                    onChange={(e) => setConfirmPassword(e.target.value)}\n                                    placeholder=\"Confirm Password\"\n                                    icon={<LockIcon />}\n                                />\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div>\n                                <button\n                                    type=\"submit\"\n                                    className=\"group relative w-full flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-[#076cf0] hover:bg-[#4834fd] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#4834fd] mt-6\"\n                                >\n                                    회원가입\n                                </button>\n                            </div>\n                        </form>\n                        <div className=\"text-center\">\n                             <p className=\"mt-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600\">\n                                이미 계정이 있으신가요?{' '}\n                                <a href=\"#\" onClick={(e) => { e.preventDefault(); navigateTo('login'); }} className=\"font-medium text-[#076cf0] hover:text-[#4834fd]\">\n                                    로그인\n                                </a>\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        // --- Main App Component (Router) ---\n        const App = () => {\n            const [currentPage, setCurrentPage] = React.useState('login'); // or 'register'\n\n            const navigate = (page) => {\n                setCurrentPage(page);\n            };\n\n            if (currentPage === 'login') {\n                return <LoginPage navigateTo={navigate} />;\n            }\n\n            if (currentPage === 'register') {\n                return <RegistrationPage navigateTo={navigate} />;\n            }\n\n            return <div>Page not found</div>;\n        };\n\n        ReactDOM.render(<App />, document.getElementById('root'));\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n<review_request>\n{\n  \"title\": \"[리뷰] 광고주센터 로그인/회원가입 페이지 라우팅 구현\",\n  \"assignee\": \"dev_advisor\",\n  \"message\": \"로그인 페이지와 회원가입 페이지 간의 화면 전환 기능을 구현했습니다. React State를 사용하여 별도의 라이브러리 없이 간단한 SPA 라우팅을 적용했습니다. 코드 리뷰 부탁드립니다.\"\n}\n</review_request>",
